{
  "texts": [
    "Traditional educational models, while effective for many, often face challenges in fully supporting the vast spectrum of learning styles and paces.",
    "Herein lies the transformative potential of AI.",
    "Imagine a classroom where every query, no matter how complex or simple, is met with patience and precision.",
    "Where feedback isn't just a standardised mark, but a comprehensive breakdown tailored to an individual's strengths and weaknesses.",
    "This is the environment conversational AI can foster."
  ]
}